      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes me feel better. i was a bit worried it was something more serious but if it's just gas then i should be fine. i have some leftover oxycodone from a dental thing a few months ago though, would it be okay if i just took one of those instead of the codeine? it's much stronger so i'll definitely be able to sleep through the night.",
